# Commit Conventions

## Commit Message Format
- Make max 2 bullet points about the changes
- Add comment that the commit was created assisted by cursor

## Example Commit Messages
```
feat: add bootstrap overlay for hetzner cluster

- Create hetzner-k8s overlay with namespace and path patches
- Update kustomization to include patch configuration

# Created with assistance from Cursor
```

```
fix: correct patch file reference in kustomization

- Rename patch file from patch-cluster-config-path.yaml to patch-root-application.yaml
- Update kustomization.yaml to reference correct patch file

# Created with assistance from Cursor
```
